asset.title: Modified Chevy Camaro "Survivor" on CSS-15 Lexani Wheels
asset.description:
Click subscribe for new videos weekly!

Introducing "Survivor Camaro" by Kristen Benavides.

Kristen's love for car culture wasn’t ingrained during her youth, or inspired by silver screen chase scenes.  Her passion was inspired by the most critical time in her life -- the fight and the conquering of leukemia.  After enduring such a strenuous hardship of what sometimes can be a fatal end, Kristen survived.  Now stronger and with the battle behind, she’s moved on with a new outlook and a high performance pallet to help create awareness of what she -- and so many others have endured.

-Klaudia Black (thespeedgirls.com)

Video by Sergio Mireles
www.s-mphotography.com

IG: KC_Survivor
IG: momentum_exposure
IG: ese_cheko
IG: alben89
